room_title: Escape room "Out of the Past" by paradigmQ in Portland
room_address: 14415 SE Mill Plain Blvd #104B Vancouver, WA 98684
room_description: How you made into the old west and smack dab in the center of an old gambling hall, you just aren’t sure.  What you do know is, you’d dearly like to get back to your present.  There is one way to make it happen, but it will take all your skills and the exact right timing or you might be stuck on the prairie forever!
